text:
Campus aane pr sbse pehle tumse hi mila tha, aur aakhiri bhi tum hi the.Shuru ke ek hafta toh lgbg hum dono hi ghumte the campus akele phir wing walon se mile. 1st year ki kya hi bakchodi thi bhai, B223 epic tha. Teri PE se lekar, ENG ki classes tk hr cheez mein mze lete the tere mai aur mishra.Koi bhi seminar ho ya workshop ya DJ kahi bhi, ghus jte the. Tera confession pr nyi wli white shirt pehen kr jna, aur birthway pr woh naagin dance kbhi nhi bhulunga bhai. Abhi tera memoir pdha toh lga ki tune sbhi kuch th likh dia yr ab mai kya hi likhunga. Itna acha lga bhai ki shayad pichle ek mahine se jo depression chal rha usse thoda relief sa mil gya. Tereko toh sb pta hi hai. Bs yeah hi hai ki agar meri zindagi ki koi kitaab hogi toh B223 ka chapter sbse acha aur mazedaar hoga. Unn dino ki choti choti cheezein yaad krke itne mze aate hai bhai, kaash woh din dobara jee paate. 
First year ke baad se bhale hi room alag ho, lekin bakchodi utni hi thi. Football se lakar, MT ke pakode, cards khelna, Fests mein apna paaglon wla dance sb kuch tha isme. Haan shyd thode academic load ke chalte itna time nhi spend kr pt tha sath, but jb bhi masti ka time milta tum log saath rehte. Trip ka toh kya hi bolun, tune meri harkate waise hi likh di, late tk sote rehne se, boat wle kaand tk. Hmari 8 bje wli bs hoti thi, aur 10 bj uthte the. Yaad hai main kaise cliff ke pass ke kr baith gya tha, mereko aaj bhi samaj nhi aata mai ruk kaise pya itne km distance mein. Phir tu kooda toh thodi himmat aayi.
Intern season yaad hai bhai, tere aur shashank ki kahi shortlist nhi aa rhi thi, phir bhi mere liye hr jgh ghuma krte the. Khandu toh bhai poore time saath rha.Sahi bolun toh campus min bhot jyda low times nhi aaye mere, but it was one of those.But tum log ensure kiye ki sahi tha mai. Ab lgta hai, life mein jo hota hai ache ke liye hota hai(yahi soch kr m aaj kl din nikal rha), kitni achi Intern lg gyi finally aur realisation ho gya ki itne se toh nhi hone wla, aur mehnat chaiye. Tune toh phir kya hi mehnat ki thi summers mein, tu agar baithta placements mein toh pakka chaap deta. Bhot sahi tayari ho gyi thi teri.
 Corona ka time shyd thoda lucky tha, thoda unlucky. Shyd job nhi lg pti itni achi dono ki, agar na hota.Pr yr, Jan ke baad se bhot dukh hua. Campus ane ke baad se toh aise aise incidents ho chuke, bhot bura time chal rha hai bhai.Shyad zindagi ka sabse bura time abhi tk ka. Pr tu frequently baat kr leta tha. Abhi bhi bhot better nhi hai haalat, but kl sahi mein bhot acha hua tera memoir padh ke. Mai toh 10 June ke liye excited tha kb tera kahndu shashank mishra ram memoir ek saath ayega aur padhunga. Shyad campus khulne ki news ke baad itna excited pehli baar hua ghar pe. Yrr jldi khatam ho yr yeah sb. AB nhi ruka jta. Tu bhi Japan chala jyga, pta nhi kb mulakat hogi. Pr yaad rkhna, bhot efforts maar ke tu yahan tk aaya hai, first year mein jahan english mein problem thi, wahanse lekar third year mein baki logon ko courses pass krwane lg gya tha tu. Tera interest core mein hi tha aur mai bhot khush hun, ki tu udhar hi kaam krega. 
Zindagi ke aakhiri 2 mahine mein shyd apan ne yeah realise kiya ki zindagi aise bhi jee skte the. Aisi life chaiye bhai. Jo krna woh kro, saare dost saath. Shyd jo jo socha tha krne ka sb kr lia hoga, unn 20-30 dino mein. Mafia, carrom, IPL, cards, badminton, football..... sb tha usme. I know aise time shyd hi dobara aaye. But memories hmesha saath rhengi..... Shashank ka woh football match ka performance..epic tha bhai. Woh race H12 ke pass, kuch bhi krwa lo humse.
Mujhe pta hai tu call krta rhega, bolna hi pdega pr phir bhi kbhi jrurat pde toh yaad kr lena. Mujhe toh shyd bhot pdne wli hai, inn dino. Japani girlfriend lao bhai, milwo hme nhi.
PS: Jldi se shadi kr lo bhai, ab toh tumhari shaadi mein dance krna hai.
PPS: Japan mein bhot kami hai male actors ki. Mishra bhi wait kr rha, bola pehli video tumhari hi dekhega.

"Bhai DS ka assignment krna hai, 12 bje deadline hai". Shyd mile hum tumse pehle bhi honge, pr baatein toh yahi se chalu hui. Tumhre campus ka shyd best time chal rha tha. Shashank nhi hota toh shyd hum tumko kbhi jan bhi nhi paate. Yaad hai ek raat ko baat kr rhe the, aur mishra ek kutte ke saath hi so gya tha.  Pichla ek saal toh shyd m sahi m depress ho jta, agar roj itna time pass nhi krte. Shyd roj 6-7 ghante apne video call pr hi nikalte the, pta nhi kya hi discussion chalta tha. Dil ka sahi mein bhot acha hai bhai tu, pichle ek saal mein logon se kitna kuch suna especially placement times, I know tune apni traf se poori koshish ki.Bhot bura lgta h, jb log SPO team aur tum logon ko blame krte hein, tum sb logon ne genuinely bhot acha kaam kiya hai aur pichle saalon ki teams se bhot better kiya hai.Life bhot bdi h, tujhe bhot aage jna h life mein choti- choti problems se pareshan mt hua kr. Dono ki location bhale hi alag ho, pr tujhe toh pta hi h, apan log virtually jitna touch mein rehte hein utna toh shyd log saath reh kr bhi ek dusre ko nhi jaante honge.Aur haan saari bhijwa dena, nhi toh rkhe rkhe kharab ho jygi,photo hai abhi bhi mere pass.

text: Bhai apan toh sikar ke hi hein, mera ghar toh yaad hi hoga tereko!!! Bhot mza aata tha bhai tere saath. Orientation time hi shyd baat hone lg gyi thi apni,. Phir batti ke freshers mein toh tumne kya hi dance kiya tha bhai, beech mein rokna pda üòÇ ,JK  acha tha bhai woh toh bs mze leta tha tere.
